/fuzz/Cargo.lock
# Fuzz corpus entries are generated artifacts; we keep a hand-seeded
# corpus under version control via individual `.silt` / named entries,
# but the auto-generated hex-name files are transient and would swamp
# the history. Exclude anything matching the 40-char sha-ish pattern.
/fuzz/corpus/fuzz_lexer/[0-9a-f]*
/fuzz/corpus/fuzz_parser/[0-9a-f]*
/fuzz/corpus/fuzz_roundtrip/[0-9a-f]*
/fuzz/corpus/fuzz_formatter/[0-9a-f]*
.sediment
.DS_Store
.env
.silt_history
.claude/
/output.txt
/output/reports/
